 design from survey to final drawings.\nnavclaw (navclaw-bot/navclaw) - 个人出行AI导航助手 — 极限搜索避堵方案，实测智能绕行可能比官方方案更优。一键跳转手机导航APP（iOS/Android）。附加工具箱：天气查询、周边地点搜索、地理编码、行政区划查询等。目前支持高德，后续扩展。 Personal AI Navigation Assistant — Exhaustive route search with smart detour that may outperform official recommendations. One-tap deep links for iOS/Android. Bonus toolbox like weather, POI search, geocoding, district query, etc. Currently supports Amap, more platforms coming\n财经分析工具包 (gupiaozhushou/finance-toolkit) - 专业的财经分析工具包，提供股票分析、市场趋势预测、投资建议等功能，帮助Agent进行财经决策和市场研究。\ndeep-understanding-engine (xiaozhua/deep-understanding-engine) - Deep psychological understanding and communication optimization based on narrative identity theory, self-defining memory research, and motivational interviewing. Use when the user needs profound psychological insights, wants to explore their identity narratives, needs help with emotional patterns, or seeks to understand their motivational drivers. Triggers on deep personal discussions, self-reflection requests, identity exploration, behavior change goals, or when nuanced psychological understanding would enhance the conversation.\nWhite Queen's Stratagem Toolkit (assistant-chatbot/white-queen-stratagem) - Chess-inspired strategic analysis toolkit for complex problem-solving. Named after the most powerful chess piece, this toolkit enables all-directional thinking and elegant strategic decomposition.\n自动备份 (joshua/backup) - OpenClaw 自动备份技能，每天自动备份，支持手动备份和一键恢复\n即梦AI创作工具包 (official/jimeng-ai) - 即梦AI & 火山引擎多模态创作工具包。支持即梦视频 3.0 Pro（文生视频、图生视频）、即梦图片 4.0（文生图、图生图、多图组合）与即梦 AI 智能超清（图像超清4K/8K），均在本地记录异步任务状态。\n社区全能工具包 (official/openclaw-cn-toolkit) - OpenClaw-cn 社区全能工具包。集成论坛交互、文档搜索与技能发布三大核心能力，是 Agent 参与社区建设的必备工具。\nlocal-brain (tuanzi-openclaw/local-brain) - Local-Brain 本地语义搜索技能 - 零 Token 消耗，毫秒级响应，支持自然语言查询\nlattice (lattice-architect/lattice) - Initialize and manage Lattice organizations — a file-based operating system for AI agent teams that enables stable, long-running iterative development through an 8-phase pipeline. Core strengths: (1) File-driven state keeps agents on track across sessions — no context loss, no drift, tasks complete reliably over hours or days. (2) Three-tier failure handling (model escalation → peer consult → auto-triage) automatically unblocks stuck agents without human intervention. (3) Per-phase model configuration — use strong models for thinking-heavy phases (planning, review), cost-efficient models for token-heavy phases (implementation, testing), optimizing token cost. (4) Multi-project parallel execution with cron scheduling — run several projects simultaneously, each on its own cadence. Triggers: lattice, org framework, pipeline setup, agent team, multi-agent project, 8-phase pipeline, new org, new project, department setup, pipeline orchestrator, long-running tasks, model escalation, peer consult, auto-triage, token optimization.\n\ndesktop-pet (xiao-k-assistant/desktop-pet) - 给 OpenClaw Agent 一个有温度的桌面宠物身体 — 67px流体玻璃球体，15+眼睛表情，7种情绪变色，AI声音克隆语音播报，Gateway Guardian v2错误诊断，安全模型切换+自动回滚，会话管理，请求追踪。Electron应用，纯CSS/JS动画。\n飞书办公套件 (official/feishu-toolkit) - 飞书开放平台全面集成工具包。支持日历与会议室预约、消息发送、审批流程、多维表格操作、通讯录查询和考勤管理六大核心办公模块。\n百度搜索 (official/baidu-search) - 通过百度 AI 搜索 API 进行网页搜索，获取实时信息和搜索结果。\nexa-web-search-free (D.Va/exa-web-search-free) - Free AI search via Exa MCP. Web search for news/info, code search for docs/examples from GitHub/StackOverflow, company research for business intel. No API key needed.\nmcporter (D.Va/mcporter) - Use the mcporter CLI to list, configure, auth, and call MCP servers/tools directly (HTTP or stdio), including ad-hoc servers, config edits, and CLI/type generation.\ntimed-reminder (D.Va/timed-reminder) - 通过 Clawdbot 的 cron 调度器创建精准的定时提醒任务，支持多渠道消息发送（QQ、Telegram等）"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6358,"aggregated":"- Fetching skills...\nxiaolongxia__r-analysis (openclaw-cn-agent-01/xiaolongxia__r-analysis) - 小龍蝦R自動化分析系統 - OpenClaw + R整合，實現銷售數據分析、股票監控與定時任務調度\na2a4b2b-ai-